ink\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">4</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Park Collections</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">5</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">6</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Park Type Guide</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">7</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Map &amp; Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">8</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Planning Essentials</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">9</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Expert Advice</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Freeport</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">City spotlight</p><h1>Indoor Dog Park in Freeport</h1><p class=\"hero-description\">Enjoy the nautical charm and pet-friendly community spaces of Freeport, Long Island.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Freeport, located on Long Island&#x27;s South Shore, offers a unique nautical atmosphere for pet owners. Known for its famous Nautical Mile, the village provides a vibrant setting for leashed walks along the water. Freeport&#x27;s local park system includes several community spaces where residents gather with their pets, fostering a close-knit and friendly atmosphere. The refreshing sea breezes make even the warmest summer days pleasant for outdoor exploration.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">The village&#x27;s strategic location provides easy access to larger regional parks and beaches, making it a convenient hub for active dog owners. Freeport&#x27;s commitment to community maintenance ensures that public spaces remain clean and welcoming for all visitors. Whether you&#x27;re enjoying a walk near the canal or visiting a local pet-friendly spot, Freeport offers a charming suburban experience with a distinct coastal flair.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Data refreshed weekly</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Live availability coming soon</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Freeport dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/freeport/hero.webp\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Freeport</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Freeport<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Verified ratings, review volume, and park availability updated directly from our community directory.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Community rating</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">4.5</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Average rating across every verif